{
  "name": "Supreme Weaponsmith Kit",
  "type": "tool",
  "img": "icons/containers/bags/pouch-gold-grey.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span dir=\"ltr\">This kit includes all of the necessary implements to prepare and create mundane weapons while in the presence or access of extreme heat and cooling capabilities.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Proficiency with this kit lets you add your proficiency bonus to any skill checks you make to make weapons.</span></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Also, proficiency with this kit is required to create Chakra Enhanced Weapons of any type.</span></p><p> </p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Swift Craft DC: 18.</span></p><p></p><p><span dir=\"ltr\">Gain a +1d4 bonus to all checks made to create Weapons or Weapon Seals, increase the per week Market value contribution on items you are crafting with this kit by 150 Ryo and when you make a Swift Craft check, increase the Ryo Bonus to 200 for every +3 you get over the listed DC.</span></p>",
